de.nec.nle.siafu.control.progress

Class ConsoleProgress

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.nec.nle.siafu.control.progress.ConsoleProgress
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Progress

    public class ConsoleProgress
extends Object
implements Progress
    A Progress implementation for GUI-less runs of Siafu. The reports are given by simply printing out on the text console's standard output.
    Author:
    Miquel Martin
